<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: The Lone Scrapper -->
  <VFE_TheLoneScavenger.label>拾荒者</VFE_TheLoneScavenger.label>
  <!-- EN: During your travels across the surface looking for pieces of scrap metal to sell in one of the outlander settlements, you stumble across an unbelievable sight: an abandoned, fully automated factory. Your scrapper senses urge you to break it apart and salvage what you can, but your inner entrepreneur desires to hear the machines sing once again.\n\nNote: Since your starting character will lack some skills, this is a difficult scenario in the early game. -->
  <VFE_TheLoneScavenger.description>你是一个拾荒者，在荒野上搜索废铜烂铁以卖给外来者谋生，这次工作中，你却看到了一副不可思议的景象：一座尚在运转的自动工厂！理性告诉你你该拆毁出一些零件继续本职工作，但感性告诉你，该让这些机器再次引吭高歌。\n\n注意：你的开局只有一个人且缺乏部分技能，这是一个较难的剧本。</VFE_TheLoneScavenger.description>
  <!-- EN: During your travels across the surface looking for pieces of scrap metal to sell in one of the outlander settlements, you stumble across an unbelievable sight: an abandoned, fully automated factory. Your scrapper senses urge you to break it apart and salvage what you can, but your inner entrepreneur desires to hear the machines sing once again.\n\nNote: Since your starting character will lack some skills, this is a difficult scenario in the early game. -->
  <VFE_TheLoneScavenger.scenario.description>你是一个拾荒者，在荒野上搜索废铜烂铁以卖给外来者谋生，这次工作中，你却看到了一副不可思议的景象：一座尚在运转的自动工厂！理性告诉你你该拆毁出一些零件继续本职工作，但感性告诉你，该让这些机器再次引吭高歌。\n\n注意：你的开局只有一个人且缺乏部分技能，这是一个较难的剧本。</VFE_TheLoneScavenger.scenario.description>
  <!-- EN: The Lone Scrapper -->
  <VFE_TheLoneScavenger.scenario.name>拾荒者</VFE_TheLoneScavenger.scenario.name>
  <!-- EN: Living from payday to payday, gathering valuable scrap around the planet and selling it to the highest bidder - usually junkyard owners, you never expected to come across something as valuable as a fully automated factory, utilising latest urbworld mechanoid tech.\n\nNow the choice is yours - will you disassemble it to not tempt so many raiders troubling these lands? Or will you bring the factory back to its former glory?\n -->
  <VFE_TheLoneScavenger.scenario.parts.GameStartDialog.text>一天又一天，你不断在这座星球上旅行，寻找废铜烂铁，并把它们卖掉谋生。你从没想过自己有朝一日会找到一座自动工厂，这可是城市世界的高端科技啊。现在你面临一个选择，把这些机器拆掉卖了以防止吸引太多袭击者，还是让它再临往日的辉煌？</VFE_TheLoneScavenger.scenario.parts.GameStartDialog.text>
  <!-- EN: An abandoned factory -->
  <VFE_TheLoneScavenger.scenario.parts.VFEC_AddStartingStructure.structureLabel>一座废弃工厂</VFE_TheLoneScavenger.scenario.parts.VFEC_AddStartingStructure.structureLabel>
  <!-- EN: A lone scrapper with a difficult choice. Difficult. -->
  <VFE_TheLoneScavenger.scenario.summary>一个面临选择的拾荒者。困难。</VFE_TheLoneScavenger.scenario.summary>
  
</LanguageData>